high_descs: Move to the TV stand against the wall where the remote is
Pick up the remote sitting on top of the middle of the TV stand
Carry the remote over to the chair behind the TV stand
Place the remote on top of the chair behind the plaid cushion
Move to the black end table against the wall next to the piano
Pick up the remote sitting on top of the end table
Turn around then head back to the chair where the other remote is sitting
Place the remote next to the other remote on top of the chair behind the cushion
anns.task_desc: Place two remotes on the chair

high_descs: Turn around, go straight, turn right, go forward, then turn left to face the shelf with the TV on it.
Pick up the remote on the shelf, in front of the TV.
Turn right, forward, then turn right to face the chair.
Put the remote on the chair, behind the pillow.
Turn right, go around the ottoman, then turn right to approach the table adjacent to the piano.
Pick up the remote on the table.
Turn around and go around the ottoman, to face the chair again.
Put the remote on the chair, next to the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the chair.

high_descs: move to the TV stand to the left of the arm chair
pick up a remote from the stand
move to the arm chair to the right of the TV
put the remote on the chair
move to the end table ahead of you
pick up a remote from the end table
move to the arm chair to the right of the TV
put the remote on the chair
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on a arm chair.
